Sentencas: Oxidative coupling of methane in a solid oxide fuel cell with 1 wt% Sr/La2O3-Bi2O3-Ag-YSZ (yttria stabilized zirconia) membrane was studied by the two mathematical models based on well mixed flow (CSTM) or plug Bow (PFM).
Titulo: Simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell for oxidative coupling of methane

Sentencas: The model predictions were in good agreement with the experimental results.
